    Text color: off-white / cream for premium look
    Icons should be centered and inside a soft rounded box
    
    Typography:
    
    Title: bold, large, clean (like Anton or similar)
    Description: smaller, readable, medium weight
    
    Responsive behavior:
    
    Desktop (1200px+): 4 cards in one row
    Tablet (768px–1199px): 2 cards per row
    Mobile (<768px): 1 card per row
    
    Add customization controls:
    
    Control for number of cards (max 6)
    Control icon size (desktop & mobile separately)
    Control title font size (desktop & mobile separately)
    Control description font size (desktop & mobile separately)
    Control card padding (desktop & mobile)
    Control spacing between cards
    Control border radius
    Control background colors (section + card)
    Control text alignment (center/left)
    
    Add hover effect:
    
    Slight upward movement (translateY)
    Soft shadow or glow effect
    
